-- Desktop look --
	+ Go to desktop
	+ Right click on every panel -> (bin) Remove panel
	+ Right click on desktop -> Add Panel -> Empty Panel
	+ Right click on panel -> Add widgets
		+ Add these widgets in the following order: Application Menu, Icons only task manager, System tray, Digital clock
	+ Right click on panel -> Edit Panel
		+ Make height smaller
		+ Put it on the upper screen edge
	
	+ Right click on Application Launcher on Panel -> Configure Application Dashboard/menu
		+ Show categories: Recent application(OFF), Recent documents(OFF)
		+ Search: Expand search to bookmarks, files and emails(OFF)
		+ Keyboard Shortcuts(Meta+F1)
	+ Right click on System tray -> Configure System tray
		+ Disable unneeded entries
	+ Right click on desktop -> Configure Desktop -> Wallpaper -> Change
	
-- Configure system --
	+ Open system settings
	+ Appearance
		+ Global theme -> Arc Dark(by x-varlesh-x)
		+ Plasma theme -> Arc Dark(by x-varlesh-x)
		+ Application Style
			+ Application style -> Set to Breeze
			+ Application Style -> Configure GTK Application Style -> Breeze-Dark
			+ Window Decorations -> Arc Dark(by x-varlesh-x)
			+ Icons -> Icons(Papirus-Dark)
	+ Workspace
		+ Workspace Behavior
			+ General Behavior -> Animation Speed(Instant)
			+ Desktop Effects -> Screen Edge and ther bloat(OFF)
			+ Screen Locking -> Appearance -> Change wallpaper
		+ Shortcuts
			+ Kwin
				+ Switch to Desktop num(meta + f(num))
				+ Windows to Desktop num(ctrl + f(num))
				+ Show Desktop Grid(meta + esc)
			+ Add(+) - terminator(ctrl + alt + t)
	+ Personalization
		+ Account Details -> Kde Wallet -> Enable the KDE wallet subsystem(OFF)
		+ Applications -> Set default
	+ Hardware
		+ Power Management -> Settings are device specific
		
-- Extra --
 + Remove bloatware
	+ (terminal) sudo apt remove skanlite okular vlc kate kcalc
	+ (terminal) sudo apt remove kdeconnect #optional 
  + (terminal) sudo apt autoremove
  
  + To bind a shortcut to Meta(Windows) key, just bind it to Meta+F1 which has the same effect(will work with both meta and meta+F1)
  + Cool themes - Dark Breeze, Nordic, Adapta
